data.description: 8060 Iris is a beautiful spacious home. Its most telling feature is a newly remodeled kitchen, newer Hardy Board siding, and solar panels galore. It speaks of comfort and solitude. The 2-car garage and RV pad with 40 amp hook-up can accommodate all the toys plus. It is situated in a cul de sac with established neighbors and a feeling of serenity. There is no HOA, and the backyard is well groomed with large shade trees, many perennials and no neighbors on the back side. This 2-owner home has been lived in, loved and cared for since it was built.  Come and make this your family's home.
